&amp;originHeight=924&amp;originWidth=1890&amp;size=125288&amp;width=1718\" alt=\"image.png\"></p>\n<p>于是乎，就在想能不能在语雀里写作，写完之后自动同步到Github的博客呢？年轻就要有激情，说干就干，花了一天时间，结合了yuque-hexo、travis-ci、Github-pages之后，终于跑通了整个写作、发布、自动部署的流程~<br><img src=\"https://cdn.nlark.com/yuque/0/2019/jpeg/155457/1546858544992-c921de6f-b08a-469a-bd5f-81996309443b.jpeg#align=left&amp;display=inline&amp;height=225&amp;linkTarget=_blank&amp;name=image.jpeg&amp;originHeight=225&amp;originWidth=225&amp;size=10511&amp;width=225\" alt=\"image.jpeg\"></p>\n"}],"PostAsset":[],"PostCategory":[{"post_id":"cjrhn70ro0000fcvhqghs6vq3","category_id":"cjrhn70ru0001fcvhrlbiaqyi","_id":"cjrhn70ru0004fcvhqv06t9ey"}],"PostTag":[{"post_id":"cjrhn70ro0000fcvhqghs6vq3","tag_id":"cjrhna9uj0000lsvh5neozymj","_id":"cjrhna9uj0001lsvhzsf53v4q"}],"Tag":[{"name":"Vue","_id":"cjrhn70ru0002fcvhgd62ypn6"},{"name":"Hexo","_id":"cjrhna9uj0000lsvh5neozymj"}]}}